    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or mark to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection, this is the one! Come by and take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
