      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained with an impeccable service history, every detail reflects a standard of excellence synonymous with collector-grade quality. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of automotive engineering, offered for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection.",
