    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a recently overhauled double-VANOS system and a fully reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise gates, paired with a factory variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling these cars are known for. Finished in a concours-level exterior with a pristine interior, this example represents a rare opportunity to own a purist-spec M-car with zero mechanical debt and a comprehensive service dossier.",
